Usage: restore_power_database [-help] -file <string> [-hierarchy <string>]
                              [-hierarchy_separator <string>]

-help                          # Prints out the command usage
-file <string>                 # Specifies the name of the power database file
                               # (string, required)
-hierarchy <string>            # Specifies to map each instance in the file
                               # with a prefixN/instance (for example,
                               # prefixA/inst) in the flat netlist, where '/'
                               # is the hierarchy seperator. Default : all.
                               # prefix (string, optional)
-hierarchy_separator <string>  # Specifies the separator character in the
                               # hierarchical net names, bus names, and pin
                               # names. Default : slash ( / ) (string, optional)